---
<Layout title="Hama & Penyakit - SiPETA Cuaca Tani">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto p-4 sm:p-6 space-y-8">
        <header class="fade-in text-center">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-black">Kenali Hama & Penyakit Utama</h1>
            <p class="text-black mt-2">Identifikasi dan cara penanganan hama & penyakit pada tanaman padi dan bawang merah.</p>
        </header>

        <main class="space-y-12">
            <section>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-800 mb-2">ğŸŒ¾ Tanaman Padi</h2>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-700 mb-4 border-l-4 border-green-800 pl-3">Hama</h3>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
                    {hamaPadi.map(item => (
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                            <img src={item.gambar} alt={item.nama} class="w-full h-48 object-cover"/>
                            <div class="p-4">
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-black">{item.nama}</h4>
                                <p class="text-xs text-black mt-2"><strong>Gejala:</strong> {item.gejala}</p>
                                <p class="text-xs text-black mt-2"><strong>Penanganan:</strong> {item.penanganan}</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    ))}
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-700 mb-4 border-l-4 border-green-800 pl-3">Penyakit</h3>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    {penyakitPadi.map(item => (
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                            <img src={item.gambar} alt={item.nama} class="w-full h-48 object-cover"/>
                            <div class="p-4">
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-black">{item.nama}</h4>
                                <p class="text-xs text-black mt-2"><strong>Gejala:</strong> {item.gejala}</p>
                                <p class="text-xs text-black mt-2"><strong>Penanganan:</strong> {item.penanganan}</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    ))}
                </div>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-red-800 mb-2">ğŸ§… Tanaman Bawang Merah</h2>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-700 mb-4 border-l-4 border-red-800 pl-3">Hama</h3>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
                    {hamaBawang.map(item => (
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                            <img src={item.gambar} alt={item.nama} class="w-full h-48 object-cover"/>
                            <div class="p-4">
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-black">{item.nama}</h4>
                                <p class="text-xs text-black mt-2"><strong>Gejala:</strong> {item.gejala}</p>
                                <p class="text-xs text-black mt-2"><strong>Penanganan:</strong> {item.penanganan}</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    ))}
                </div>
                 <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neutral-700 mb-4 border-l-4 border-red-800 pl-3">Penyakit</h3>
                 <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    {penyakitBawang.map(item => (
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                            <img src={item.gambar} alt={item.nama} class="w-full h-48 object-cover"/>
                            <div class="p-4">
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg text-black">{item.nama}</h4>
                                <p class="text-xs text-black mt-2"><strong>Gejala:</strong> {item.gejala}</p>
                                <p class="text-xs text-black mt-2"><strong>Penanganan:</strong> {item.penanganan}</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    ))}
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <p class="text-center text-xs text-neutral-500 pt-4"><strong>Catatan:</strong> Gambar yang ditampilkan adalah ilustrasi. Untuk hasil identifikasi yang akurat, konsultasikan dengan Petugas Penyuluh Lapangan (PPL) setempat.</p>
    </div>
</Layout>